Cursed Earth Figure Viewer
============================

Figure Viewer - control Evil Islands figures.

Figure Viewer is part of Cursed Earth spikes.
Check http://cursedearth.sourceforge.net/ for more details.

Try figviewer -h for help.

Some examples:
figviewer --ei-path=c:\evil_islands --primary-texture=rick unmori
figviewer --ei-path=/home/user/evil_islands --primary-texture=troll00 --animation-name=uattack unmotr
figviewer --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=dragon01 --animation-name=cidle unmodg
figviewer -f --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=dragon01 --animation-name=ubriefing01 unmodg
figviewer -f --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=succubus00 --animation-name=cidle unmosu
figviewer --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=troll00 --animation-name=uattack unmotr
figviewer --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=lizardman00 --animation-name=cidle01 unmoli
figviewer --ei-path=/path/to/evil_islands --primary-texture=mainmenu00 --secondary-texture=mainmenu00labels unmoco2
